<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪不敢相信自己的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地上有很多呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有大呼啦圈、小呼啦圈、彩色的呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师！您怎么知道？” 莉琪大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你好，莉琪。知道什么？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢呼啦圈！” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上个星期的生日，我收到了一个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是吗？那太好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天你会学到一些呼啦圈游戏。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“游戏？” 莉琪皱了皱眉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是喜欢转呼啦圈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“穿上外套，拿一个呼啦圈。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪拿了一个有绿色和粉色条纹的呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天很阴。” 尼娜搓着手说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放下呼啦圈。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“手拉手围成一个圈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>什么时候才能转呼啦圈呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第一个活动，我们要一起合作。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以站在这里吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到莉琪和贾森中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拉起贾森的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在拉莉琪的手之前，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在手臂上挂了个呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要传递呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，不能放手。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？那要怎么传递？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会知道的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师低下肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼啦圈滑到莉琪的左臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪把头穿过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她扭动身体穿过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把腿伸出去，呼啦圈到了她的右臂！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我成功了！” 她尖叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，到你了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜也跟莉琪一样穿了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，呼啦圈就到了波比的手臂上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比传给伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦传给贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森传给雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼啦圈传了一圈！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们成功了！” 贾森大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家是怎么做到的？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比大声说：“我得看尼娜的动作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果她弯下身，我也得弯下身。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最难的部分就是不能放手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们什么时候可以转呼啦圈呢？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快了。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在地上滚呼啦圈，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后在它停下来的地方转呼啦圈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪脱下外套，颤抖着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的呼啦圈在地上滚，她跟着它跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当呼啦圈停下来时，她转起呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼啦圈转呀转，真有意思！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她好像在一个呼啦圈的乐园里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她也在转呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男生们的呼啦圈却一直掉下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪觉得，她可以一直转下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天在变黑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，有个湿湿的东西落到她的脸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “是雪花！” 尼娜大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下雪了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从来没见过雪！” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很喜欢雪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呼啦圈真好玩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在雪里转呼啦圈更好玩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>